content: dxganta: Opened one PR (#2820) introducing a new ParaSwap API-based swap action for the EVM plugin, with substantial code changes (+225,275/-13,175 lines) across 1,931 files. Created and helped close issue #2661 regarding an error in the EVM plugin's swap handler, contributing comments on two issues. Activity was sporadic, with contributions on only 2 days this month, primarily focused on new feature development.
